title: José Antonio Llamas
text:
José Antonio Llamas Martínez (born 28 February 1985) is a Spanish <a href="Association%20football">footballer</a> who plays for <a href="UE%20Sant%20Andreu">UE Sant Andreu</a> as a <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29%23Full-back">right back</a>.
Honours.
Spain U17
